    "description": "<strong>Time Survivors</strong>是史上最不符合历史事实的Roguelike游戏，您可以<strong>扮演像Abe Lincoln、Tesla、Cleopatra这样的传奇历史人物</strong>，现在每个人都拥有改变游戏的独特能力。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211390/extras/e29ef44726af23b56fe87f5eb867e63c.webp?t=1728313551\" width=610 height=45 /></span><br><br>扮演织田信长，变成飞行的忍者机器人，或者像Abe Lincoln一样，用樱桃树制造防御障碍（历史上不准确™），或者像Nero一样点燃战场-选择权在您手中。每个角色在<strong>每次运行中都带来独特的感觉</strong>，使每次玩耍都成为独特的冒险。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211390/extras/8fab3f7a41d30e949047f9d6f57af156.poster.avif?t=1728313551\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211390/extras/8fab3f7a41d30e949047f9d6f57af156.webm?t=1728313551\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>穿越时间，解开谜团的同时<strong>与众多令人难忘的敌人战斗</strong>。超过150种不同的武器，物品，圣物和增益供您选择，每次运行都是独特的体验。在中世纪与骷髅战斗，在石器时代与Velociraptors和T-Rex战斗，并在途中发现很多任务和秘密。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211390/extras/568fd7ae3f31f8547281a0a9dc2c6ae2.webp?t=1728313551\" width=610 height=45 /></span><br><br>但这还不是全部 - Time Survivors引入了一个新的元进度系统，允许您使用在运行过程中收集的黄金和其他资源解锁和升级角色、武器，甚至<strong>游戏模式修饰符</strong>。根据您喜欢的游戏风格定制您的进度，并策略性地<strong>分配资源</strong>以创建自己的破坏性构建。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211390/extras/6e00ba7817b70e2fd4cc9192b20ba1a4.poster.avif?t=1728313551\" width=620 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211390/extras/6e00ba7817b70e2fd4cc9192b20ba1a4.webm?t=1728313551\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211390/extras/6e00ba7817b70e2fd4cc9192b20ba1a4.mp4?t=1728313551\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211390/extras/6b04eaad05448a709ae7731255a655a7.webp?t=1728313551\" width=610 height=45 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>扮演具有独特能力的史诗般的历史人物<br></li><li>历史不准确的阶段，如石器时代、黑暗时代、古埃及等，充满了敌人、秘密、小boss和终极boss<br></li><li>基于技能树的游戏元素的元进度<br></li><li>从中选择为每次运行提供独特体验的数百种不同的武器、增益、被诅咒的圣物、强化和可解锁物品<br></li><li>休闲快速的20分钟游戏会话+很多要发现的任务和秘密<br></li><li>沙盒模式，用于测试任何超强构建并针对任何敌人进行培训</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211390/extras/f420ded95cbbf8b53f377e71e7a10909.poster.avif?t=1728313551\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211390/extras/f420ded95cbbf8b53f377e71e7a10909.webm?t=1728313551\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>既然您已经来到这里...请不要忘记将其添加到愿望清单中并关注此页面，以随时了解最新功能和更新！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211390/extras/e95bb319e2b091396922b17f6a273a3f.poster.avif?t=1728313551\" width=612 height=92 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211390/extras/e95bb319e2b091396922b17f6a273a3f.webm?t=1728313551\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211390/extras/e95bb319e2b091396922b17f6a273a3f.mp4?t=1728313551\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
